Bors-Pantheon <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/ukillingu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Killingu</A> at: 6/27/02 2:34:48 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/ubaym.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Baym</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/27/02 2:24:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3639.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> Most SBs are considering going LA because of the liability of using a 2hander in combat. Yes, 2handers are a realm ability, but IMO they are of marginal benefit to SBs. Pure critblades are a dying bread since the one shot stealth nerf. We will see that for sure upon respect.<br>
<br>
